.Dd March 2, 2026
.Dt PKG-HELP 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm "pkg help"
.Nd display usage information for pkg commands
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar command
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is used to display the manual page for a
.Xr pkg 8
command.
When invoked with a valid command name,
.Nm
opens the corresponding manual page using
.Xr man 1 .
.Pp
If the specified command is an alias defined in
.Xr pkg.conf 5 ,
.Nm
displays the alias expansion instead.
.Pp
When invoked without arguments,
.Nm
displays a brief usage summary of all available
.Xr pkg 8
commands.
.Sh EXAMPLES
Display the manual page for the
.Cm install
command:
.Dl $ pkg help install
.Pp
Display the manual page for
.Xr pkg.conf 5 :
.Dl $ pkg help pkg.conf
.Pp
Display all available commands:
.Dl $ pkg help
